reviewText:
15 Cool Episodes:
1. Fresh Hare (1942). Bugs and elmer fudd.
2. Always Kickin' (1939) Hunky and spunky.
3. The Wabbit Who Came to Supper (1942) Bugs and elmer fudd.
4. Case of the Missing Hare (1942) Ala bahma and bugs bunny.
5. Wackiki Wabbit (1943) Bugs bunny and the 2 castaways.
6. Peeping Penguins (1937) The Four Penguins.
7. Four Musicians of Bremen (1922) A Walt Disney Cartoon.
8. Slick Sleuths (1926) Mutt And Jeff.
9. Emerald Isle  (1949) Sreen songs.
10. The Hunting Season (1935) Molly Moo Cow.
11. Spree Lunch (1957) Popeye The Sailor Man.
12. Helter Swelter (1950) Screen Songs.
13. It's a Greek Life (1936) Van Beuren.
14. An Itch in Time (1943) Elmer Fudd.
15. Flop Goes the Weasel (1943) Merrie Melodies.
And My Son Loves This DVD Too.
